<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">قال الله عزَّ وجلَّ:</span> <span class="c2">(وَاسْجُدْ وَاقْتَرِبْ (١٩)</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">الأم:</span> باب <span class="c2">(الذكر في السجود)</span> :<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
